;A healthy Internet is created and owned by us all
Zdrav internet je stvoren i posjedovan od svih nas


;The Internet owes much of its success to openness: its open, shared structure has made it easy for everyone to build, surf, and thrive on it. But a few big companies are closing in, closing doors, and creating walled gardens that concentrate their ownership and control of the Web. Together, we can fight to make sure no one limits our Internet access, experience, or creation.
Internet duguje mnogo od svog uspjeha prema otvorenosti: otvoren je, zajednička struktura je učinila jednostavnim za sve da grade, surfaju, i napreduju na njemu. Ali nekoliko velikih kompanija se približavaju, zatvaranjem vrata, i stvaranjem ograđenih parkova koji koncentriraju njihovo vlasništvo i kontrolu weba. Zajedno, možemo se boriti da budemo sigurni da niko neće ograničiti naš internet pristup, iskustvo i kreaciju.


